# 📘 PRODUCT REQUIREMENTS DOCUMENT (PRD)

## Slotify – Scheduling & Booking Platform

---

## 1. Product Overview

Slotify is a full-stack scheduling platform inspired by Calendly that enables users to create event types, define availability, and allow others to book meetings through a public booking link. The system focuses on simplicity, flexibility, and scalability while supporting advanced scheduling features such as buffer times, availability overrides, and rescheduling.

---

## 2. Problem Statement

Scheduling meetings manually involves back-and-forth communication, leading to inefficiency, missed opportunities, and time conflicts.

Slotify solves this by:

* Automating availability sharing
* Allowing self-service booking
* Preventing scheduling conflicts
* Streamlining meeting coordination

---

## 3. Goals & Objectives

### Primary Goals

* Enable seamless meeting scheduling without manual coordination
* Provide a clean, intuitive user experience
* Ensure accurate time slot management with no overlaps

### Secondary Goals

* Support advanced scheduling features
